      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2021-04-16</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2021-09-24T15:59:45Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Investor Choice Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits broker-dealers and investment advisers from including mandatory arbitration, forum selection restrictions, or bans on class action suits in a customer or client agreement. Issuers of securities are also prohibited from mandating arbitration in a shareholder agreement.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
